  <description><![CDATA[<p>The charming Hotel Scoiattolo (Squirrel) offers its guests good accommodation in the heart of Courmayeur, right opposite Bollino park. Just 100m from the pedestrian centre, both the Courmayeur and Dolonne cable cars are 10 minutes' walk away - hotel runs a free shuttle service. Enjoy views of Mont Blanc and the surrounding mountains from every angle. You may upgrade locally to take dinner at the hotel’s elegant ‘Al Torchio’ restaurant specialising in typical Aostan dishes using locally sourced ingredients. T<span>he team at the Scoiattolo pride themselves on providing good food and a great service - the perfect combination for any ski hotel!</span></p>
<p> </p>]]></description>
